#-------------------------
.vscode
**/*-v[0-9].*
**/*-v[0-9][0-9].*
**/*-v[0-9]
**/*-v[0-9][0-9]
**/*-dev
**/dev*.*
/tests
/test
/docs


# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
.env*

# vercel
.vercel

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

.aiexclude

